snippet.title: Super Animal Royale - Announce Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Fight for FUR-vival! 

Super Animal Royale is a 2D top-down Battle Royale coming later this year on PS5 and PS4. Collect, loot, and shoot your way to the top of the food chain!

Join the Super Animal Royale Community
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/animalroyale
Twitter:https://twitter.com/animalroyale
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/animalroyale/
